#set text(font: "Avenir Next", size: 10pt)
#set par(leading: 0.5em)
#show heading: set block(above: 1.4em, below: 0.4em)
#set page(
  paper: "a4",
  margin: (top: 2.5cm, left: 1.5cm, right: 1.5cm, bottom: 2.5cm),
  header: context {
    set text(size: 9pt, fill: luma(80))
    grid(
      columns: (1fr, auto, auto),
      align: (left + horizon, right + horizon, right + horizon),
      column-gutter: 8pt,
      [*Bonucakes - Saundersfoot Trip*],
      [Charted Consultants],
      image("logo.png", height: 14pt)
    )
    line(length: 100%, stroke: 0.5pt + luma(80))
  },
  footer: context {
    set text(size: 9pt, fill: luma(80))
    align(center)[Page #counter(page).display() of #counter(page).final().at(0)]
  }
)
#set heading(numbering: none)

// Title
#align(center)[
  #text(size: 22pt, weight: "bold", fill: rgb("#1e3a5f"))[Saundersfoot Trip Checklist]
  #v(0.2cm)
  #text(size: 11pt, fill: luma(60))[27 Feb - 5 Mar 2026]
]

#v(0.5cm)

= Website Work

- [ ] Review current Bonucakes website
- [ ] Prepare development setup
- [ ] Gather design inspiration
- [ ] List questions for Minh Uyên

= Content Inventory

- [ ] Collect existing videos from past years
- [ ] Collect existing photos and media assets
- [ ] Organise content by type/date/topic
- [ ] Identify content that needs editing
- [ ] Create content library structure

= Workshop Preparation (Sunday 1 Mar 9pm)

- [ ] Draft workshop outline and key topics
- [ ] Prepare slides/presentation materials
- [ ] Test livestream equipment and connection
- [ ] Set up voice recording for full session capture
- [ ] Set up video recording with professional lighting
- [ ] Test multi-track recording setup
- [ ] Prepare follow-up materials for attendees
- [ ] Practice run-through

= Vietnam Team Call (Tuesday 12pm UK / 7pm VN)

- [ ] Schedule call with Vietnam team
- [ ] Prepare agenda for team discussion
- [ ] Test video conferencing setup
- [ ] Share any materials needed for the call
- [ ] Prepare updates on website progress

= Filming Equipment

- [ ] Camera equipment (main camera + backup)
- [ ] Lighting equipment (portable lights for indoor shoots)
- [ ] Microphone for audio (clip-on + shotgun)
- [ ] Dedicated voice recorder for workshop audio capture
- [ ] Tripods/stabilizers
- [ ] Extra batteries and memory cards
- [ ] Lens cleaning kit
- [ ] Multi-track recording setup for workshop

= Packing List

*Tech & Work:*
- [ ] Laptop + charger
- [ ] External hard drive for content backup
- [ ] USB drives
- [ ] Headphones
- [ ] Notebook and pens
- [ ] Phone charger + power bank

*Filming:*
- [ ] All filming equipment (see Filming Equipment section)
- [ ] Camera bags
- [ ] Backdrop/reflector (if needed)

*Personal:*
- [ ] Clothes for 6 days
- [ ] Toiletries
- [ ] Medications (if any)
- [ ] Comfortable shoes for beach walks
- [ ] Jacket/warm clothing (Wales in Feb/Mar)

= Travel & Logistics

- [ ] Confirm accommodation details
- [ ] Plan driving route to Saundersfoot
- [ ] Check car before trip (fuel, tyre pressure, etc.)
- [ ] Download offline maps
- [ ] Pack snacks/drinks for drive
- [ ] Plan restaurant reservations for the week

= Pre-Trip Tasks

*Week Before:*
- [ ] Test all equipment (cameras, lights, microphones)
- [ ] Charge all batteries
- [ ] Format memory cards
- [ ] Update laptop software
- [ ] Backup current work

*Day Before:*
- [ ] Pack everything
- [ ] Check weather forecast
- [ ] Confirm accommodation check-in time
- [ ] Print agenda and checklist (optional)
- [ ] Get cash for the trip

= During Trip - Daily Checks

- [ ] Backup all filmed content daily
- [ ] Charge equipment overnight
- [ ] Review footage from each shoot
- [ ] Keep notes on content ideas
- [ ] Track expenses

= Post-Trip Follow-up

- [ ] Organise all filmed content
- [ ] Edit priority footage
- [ ] Process workshop audio and video recordings
- [ ] Create reusable content clips from workshop
- [ ] Follow up with Vietnam team on action items
- [ ] Continue website development
- [ ] Send workshop recording/materials to attendees
- [ ] Thank you message to Minh Uyên

#v(1cm)
#align(center)[
  #text(size: 9pt, fill: luma(100), style: "italic")[
    Print this checklist and tick off items as you complete them.
  ]
]
